{"tid":1931173,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"拒招待武漢肺炎或疑似武漢肺炎不違反《殘疾歧視條例》","createTime":"2020-03-18T04:37:33.000Z","updateTime":"2020-03-19T08:48:48.000Z","uid":79563,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"a4dfb0842aec0ee340c1f88b434c6afa87fbccf2","tid":1931173,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T04:37:33.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第487章 《殘疾歧視條例》</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n61.傳染病<br />\n(1)除第(2)款另有規定外，如 &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)某人的殘疾屬任何<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳染病</span></span></strong>；及<br />\n(b)有關的歧視性作為是<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">為保護公眾健康屬合理地需要的</span></span></strong>，<br />\n則即使另一人歧視該殘疾的人，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">本條例並不適用</span></span></strong>於該另一人。<br />\n<br />\n(2)為免生疑問，現聲明︰任何人凡對人類免疫力病毒測試呈陽性反應或患上名為&ldquo;後天免疫力缺乏症&rdquo;的病症(一般稱為&ldquo;愛滋病&rdquo;)，第(1)款並不只因該人有該情況此一事實而適用於該人。<br />\n<br />\n(3)<br />\n在本條中，<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">傳染病 (infectious disease)包括</span></span></strong> &mdash;&mdash;<br />\n(a)<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">《預防及控制疾病條例》(第599章)所指的任何表列傳染病或由表列傳染性病原體引致的疾病</span></span></strong>；及 (由2008年第14號第18條代替)<br />\n(b)由衞生署署長藉憲報公告所指明的可傳播的疾病。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">第599章 《預防及控制疾病條例》</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n附表1 [第2及15條] 表列傳染病<br />\n<br />\n34AAA<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">.嚴重新型傳染性病原體呼吸系統病 (Severe respiratory disease associated with a novel infectious agent) (由2020年第3號法律公告增補)</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"535ade791692cb25b201c3dce0e525f808cfb990","tid":1931173,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-18T05:53:38.000Z","msg":"睇返最近三任嘅平機會主席，就知呢個位係退休官員嘅俱樂部，現任主席上任差不多一年，對歧視條例都依然唔熟，乜都估估下，上星期就話唔違反任何現有歧視範疇，今個星期就砌條&quot;莫須有&quot;出嚟<br />\n<br />\n話唔俾大劣人幫襯，可能係殘疾歧視，咁平機會主席間接標籤所有大劣人係殘疾人士 (如果唔係，點樣構成殘疾歧視先?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />)，佢自己係唔係歧視大劣人嘅final boss?"},{"pid":"f738e8ecf4d9718aa71ff7f4d0fbd2f35b4b983b","tid":1931173,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:55:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0daf8d77e2eca3c13f8bd0c1f231d271890f7cac","tid":1931173,"uid":306914,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T04:59:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 平機會食屎啦，故意誤導公眾"},{"pid":"ef7d123618b39c0d92adecb72788fb3af21cc393","tid":1931173,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:06:48.000Z","msg":"平機會主席朱敏健表示，平機會已接獲近600宗與餐廳拒絕招待內地客或涉及歧視的投訴和查詢，相信數字仍會再上升。他表示，如果以防疫原因不招待，屬於有合理需要，不屬於殘疾歧視，平機會暫時亦未接獲有關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515471-20200319.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515471-20200319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=V4yVQ1MiaEIlcmjbsyBqF4%2FGH25nCqGTJutLbOxS7Ms%3D&h=3b00a711\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1515471-20200319.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=82c5fce1\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1515471-20200319.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"78b86ce31c484e45ca5496d14f38224bb9f1b8e1","tid":1931173,"uid":35456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:07:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11e20d153bd85ae0db3f89b746961882b99d9c32","tid":1931173,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:45:23.000Z","msg":"終審法院於○五年判決時，為「公職人員行為失當罪」定下五項犯罪元素定義，包括：<br />\n一、身為公職人員；<br />\n二、在執行公職的過程中或在與其公職有關情況下；<br />\n三、蓄意作出失當行為，或不作出恰當行為，如蓄意疏忽職守或不履行職務；<br />\n四、沒有合理解釋或理由；<br />\n五、其行為偏離公職職責範圍或宗旨屬於嚴重而非微不足道。"},{"pid":"dadbbc3c877f307b9cc3ac0a161d6677246fec14","tid":1931173,"uid":132283,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-19T08:48:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}